Transcription.Text: Creature of habit. We cannot refuse him our pity. He worked himself to death at a Herculean task for which he was fitted by neither character nor experience. We must remember at the same time that he had been for the previous twentyeight years Secretary at the horse g ards apparently without attempting any reform in the administration of the army.
